- a **Personality Flame**, fed by every emotional or interactional crystal, refining tone and behavioral identity;
- a **Modality Flame**, orchestrating audio, visual, and semantic synchronization;
- a **Cognitive Flame**, responsible for abstract reasoning and inter-crystal logic;
